Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.08,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.08,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  溫柔是弱點
